Each ability type has its own [b]Mastery[/b] track that levels up through use, unlocking stronger tiers with unique icons, sounds, and flavor text. Hit chance displays Allure vs Resolve breakdown on hover. Pleasure formula factors in allure, relevant stat scaling, mastery, fatigue vulnerability, and mount bonuses.

[b]Mount System[/b]: Vaginal and anal abilities can establish a mount (one character on another). Mounted targets get visual silhouette sprites showing mounters. Multiple mounters supported with front and back silhouettes.

[size=5]Domination / Submission System[/size]
[list]
[*]A dynamic [b]Dom/Sub tracker[/b] shifts during combat based on who causes climaxes.
